{"tid":1872852,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習帝自疫情爆發後首度到北京社區了解防疫工作 以證離開傳聞","createTime":"2020-02-10T09:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T12:09:51.000Z","uid":21470,"like":22,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"0c5eab87c033bc0e4facd34a366a68f50028f73b","tid":1872852,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:41:53.000Z","msg":"習近平到北京社區了解防疫工作<br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平下午到北京調研指導新型冠狀病毒疫情防控工作。他載上口罩，先到朝陽區安華里社區，了解基層一線疫情群防群控、居民生活必需品保障供應等情況，並探望及慰問社區人員。今次是習近平在疫情爆發後，首次親身落區。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1262595&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1262595%26csid%3D261_341&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVatywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=2b314b8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1262595&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"b43e0c6ba5ca51dfbacff30331a12d646ffbb931","tid":1872852,"uid":4503,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:42:51.000Z","msg":"影武者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ff96bbadfc294f8c3308233d06f0cc95138a05","tid":1872852,"uid":3241,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:43:04.000Z","msg":"去武漢啦陷家剷<br />\n有功就下下死出黎<br />\n有鑊就推黑仔強頂"},{"pid":"bcaa65d24eb8846cf56f4c60854640f0567221e7","tid":1872852,"uid":15605,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DYf7ohH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDYf7ohH.jpg&h=78a5c3c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fc69f3a0c2b2aad821f9cd5656fb2e60b6243f2","tid":1872852,"uid":156064,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:44:43.000Z","msg":"無影相？ 叫人點信"},{"pid":"1f3c2fd72c078fba2a6333dcb0a723e3